#summary Benchmark results for Q
= Introduction =
This is the results computed using JMatrixBenchmark in early September 2009.  These plots show relative performance as a function of matrix size.  All performance is relative to EJML.  

Tests were performed on: Vista 64bit, JVM 1.6.0\_16, Intel Q9400 Quad 2.66 GHz.

For more information on how the tests were performed and comments about why/how
these tests were performed see the benchmark document on the main page.
